javax.accessibility.Accessible, java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable
class ResourceList
extends javax.swing.JPanel

The list of RDF resources for the main app window. This list appears on the right-hand side of the main app window and contains a list of all resources in the currently loaded RDF/XML file (it is blank if no file is currently loaded). It allows users to select resource and modify or remove them. There is also a button to add new resources.
